overview: A wildlife enthusiast, Jean-Pierre Bosquet brings us on a journey to Singapore's Sungei Buloh Wetland Reserve to uncover some of the unknown nature in the midst of our metropolis city. Subaraj Rajathurai, a veteran wildlife consultant speaks on behalf of these animals and the threats they face.

production_companies.name: Ngee Ann Polytechnic, School of Film & Media Studies

tagline: Explore  the  unknown  nature  of  Singapore  and  the  threats faced by its wildlife.
title: Unknownature
